                                                     ("single","status is single"),
                                                     ("divorced","status is divorced")])

sql1 = "select * from homework.bank where marital = '"+choice1+"'"

print("Your choice was " + choice1)
print("Your SQL is [" + sql1 + "]")

z.show(
    spark.sql(sql1)
    )
